Privacy Policy for Gudi Good
Effective Date: February 14, 2024
Welcome to Gudi Good, developed by Thonburi Healthcare Group. This Privacy Policy informs you of our policies regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of personal data when you use our Service and the choices you have associated with that data.
Collection and Use of Information
Personal Information
We collect information that you provide directly to us, such as when you create an account, interact with our app, or make in-app purchases. This may include:
• Name
• Email address
Sign-In Information
Gudi Good allows sign-in through Google and Apple, collecting information like your email address, name, and profile picture, as permitted by your sign-in settings.
Log Data and Cookies
We collect information that your browser sends whenever you visit our Service or when you access the Service by or through a mobile device.
In-App Purchases (IAP)
Our app offers IAPs handled by the app store (Google Play, Apple App Store). We receive information about the purchase but not your payment details.
Use of Data
Gudi Good uses the collected data for various purposes:
• To provide and maintain our Service
• To notify you about changes to our Service
• To allow you to participate in interactive features of our Service
• To provide customer support
• To gather analysis or valuable information so that we can improve our Service
• To monitor the usage of our Service
• To detect, prevent, and address technical issues
Sharing of Information
We may share your information with third parties in the following ways:
• With Service Providers: To facilitate our Service, to provide the Service on our behalf, or to assist us in analyzing how our Service is used.
• For Legal Reasons: To comply with legal obligations, protect and defend our rights or property, prevent or investigate possible wrongdoing, protect the personal safety of users, or protect against legal liability.
Security of Data
The security of your data is important to us, but remember that no method of transmission over the Internet or method of electronic storage is 100% secure. We strive to use commercially acceptable means to protect your Personal Information.
Children's Privacy
Our Service does not address anyone under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personally identifiable information from children under 13.
Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page and updating the "effective date" at the top of this Privacy Policy.
Compliance with Google Play and Apple Guidelines
This Privacy Policy complies with Google Play's User Data policy and Apple's guidelines, ensuring the privacy and security of user data collected through the Gudi Good app.
Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us:
Email:
communications@thg.co.th
Address: 34/1 Itsaraphap Rd, Ban Chang Lor, Bangkok Noi, Bangkok 10700
Effective Date: February 14, 2024
